This paper discusses the improvement of performance and security in the Tor network, which involves computer security (cs.CR) and networking (cs.NI). The proposed algorithm also considers the bandwidth and uptime of relays, which are related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and system and network optimization (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of a software upgrade on the client side, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
